            {
              "textEn": "<b>Lesson 8 • Discussing a difficult decision</b>"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "paragraphs": [
            {
              "textEn": "Anna, Lynn, and Jeff are thinking about moving their manufacturing facilities from the United States to China. Jeff is having trouble deciding what to do."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "paragraphs": [
            {
              "textEn": "<b>Anna:</b> We need to decide already whether or not we want to move our manufacturing from the United States to China. Jeff, have you made the final decision?"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "paragraphs": [
            {
              "textEn": "<b>Jeff:</b> There are"
            },
            {
              "keyword": "pros and cons",
              "word": "pros and cons"
            },
            {
              "textEn": "to moving it to China. I've been"
            },
            {
              "keyword": "back and forth",
              "word": "back and forth"
            },
            {
              "textEn": "on this issue for months. I'm"
            },
            {
              "keyword": " of two minds",
              "word": " of two minds"
            },
            {
              "textEn": "."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "paragraphs": [
            {
              "textEn": "<b>Anna:</b> Jeff, I know this is a"
            },
            {
              "keyword": "tough call",
              "word": "tough call"
            },
            {
              "textEn": ", but now is not the time to be"
            },
            {
              "keyword": "wishy-washy",
              "word": "wishy-washy"
            },
            {
              "textEn": ". We need to make a decision."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "paragraphs": [
            {
              "textEn": "<b>Lynn:</b> That's right, and I recommend we"
            },
            {
              "keyword": "bite the bullet",
              "word": "bite the bullet"
            },
            {
              "textEn": "and move our operations to China."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "paragraphs": [
            {
              "textEn": "<b>Anna:</b> Or we could"
            },
            {
              "keyword": "test the waters",
              "word": "test the waters"
            },
            {
              "textEn": "by moving 25 percent of our operations there."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "paragraphs": [
            {
              "textEn": "<b>Lynn:</b> Good idea. That would give us"
            },
            {
              "keyword": "the best of both worlds",
              "word": "the best of both worlds"
            },
            {
              "textEn": ": we could reduce our risk, while starting to enjoy some of the cost savings from lower-cost manufacturing."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "paragraphs": [
            {
              "textEn": "<b>Jeff:</b> I agree with you that we should"
            },
            {
              "keyword": "put a stake in the ground",
              "word": "put a stake in the ground"
            },
            {
              "textEn": ". Let's move a quarter of our operations to China."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "paragraphs": [
            {
              "textEn": "<b>Lynn:</b>"
            },
            {
              "keyword": "good call",
              "word": "Good call"
            },
            {
              "textEn": ", Jeff!"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "paragraphs": [
            {
              "textEn": "<b>Jeff:</b> I hope I don't"
            },
            {
              "keyword": "live to regret a decision",
              "word": "live to regret this decision",
              "wordAudioSrc": "/dictionary/.mp3"
            },
            {
              "textEn": "."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "paragraphs": [
            {
              "textEn": "<b>Anna:</b> You won't."
            },
            {
              "keyword": "my gut tells me",
              "word": "my gut tells me",
              "wordAudioSrc": "/dictionary/.mp3"
            },
            {
              "textEn": "we're doing the right thing."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
